headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust (FRT) Q1 FFO and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (FRT) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 0.59% and 0.72%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
